flowchart TD
    A["Process Start"] --> B["main(): Parse args + init SDL/window/render assets"]
    B --> C["Build RuntimeEngine\n(owns input orchestration + state transitions)"]
    C --> D["Enter thin main loop"]

    D --> E["main pumps SDL events"]
    E --> F["main forwards local SDL input facts to engine queue\n(non-blocking publish only)"]
    F --> G["main calls engine.tick(now)"]

    G --> H["Engine updates capture state\n(focus/cursor/capture-enabled policy)"]
    H --> I["Engine note_consumer_heartbeat()"]
    I --> J["Engine drains sanitized input events + snapshot"]

    J --> K["main renders frame from engine snapshot\n(HUD/event panel consume unified payload)"]
    K --> L["present()"]
    L --> M{"Quit requested?"}
    M -->|No| D
    M -->|Yes| Z["Shutdown + cursor restore"]

    N["CG/HID thread"] --> O["Raw global key events"]
    O --> P["Global input state machine\n(atomic mutation under lock)"]
    P --> J

    Q["Local SDL probe resolver thread"] --> R["Consume SDL alias queue"]
    R --> P

    S["Watchdog thread"] --> T{"Heartbeat stale > timeout?"}
    T -->|Yes| U["Fail-open: disable effective capture + clear held state"]
    T -->|No| V["No action"]
    U --> P
    V --> P

    W["Rule: no domain/input logic in main"] --> D
